commit.message: chore: update version to `0.10.0`

doc: updated `README.md` for cargo install to specify `--locked`
doc: updated `README.md` for version `0.10.0`

doc(net): improved doc comment for `probe.rs` module

refactor(net): renamed `MAX_SEQUENCE` as `MAX_INITIAL_SEQUENCE`
